{"tid":143472,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"西湯黎講，紅定白?","createTime":"2017-03-04T15:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T11:41:29.000Z","uid":85946,"like":155,"dislike":126,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d09c403407384833380cab3bf4d8324c508d8ec8","tid":143472,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:51:55.000Z","msg":"一般茶記，普普通通平平地既西餐廳都係得羅宋同忌廉 兩隻湯選擇<br />\n<br />\n有次我同9條友食飯，落單阿姐問咩湯，結果係九碗白，得我一碗紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上識親既人，唔知點解大部分都係鍾意飲白湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想問下，連登有冇人鍾意飲羅宋湯?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:羅宋湯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:忌廉湯"},{"pid":"77000c5659148d2adca76784eaceeea64e80fdb9","tid":143472,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"兩隻都好好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531b42aabc64a807b3bb203b43a9d8b859f5781c","tid":143472,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"茶記紅<br />\n<br />\n普通西白<br />\n<br />\n高級西紅"},{"pid":"87d5b096f14921e260e094dc0359be7ae0646774","tid":143472,"uid":83998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:55:20.000Z","msg":"細個白<br />\n大個紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a22dadfbe835e28bec651183a90e0a1726666b","tid":143472,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>茶記紅<br />\n<br />\n普通西白<br />\n<br />\n高級西紅</blockquote><br />\n高級西一定係紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8978e4acf66422741fdd08a87db5c8a97dcb6125","tid":143472,"uid